          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "More recently, former Rep. Pat Tiberi, another Ohio Republican who led the House Ways and Means Committee‚Äôs subcommittee on health and chaired the Joint Economic Committee, announced in October 2017 that he would resign his seat in January 2018 to take over the Ohio Business Roundtable, an organization whose members include many of the nation‚Äôs largest corporations. Although he notified the House Ethics Committee that he was negotiating for the position, Tiberi ",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              },
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "detail": 0,
                    "format": 0,
